<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ạ̉sjd fy kẖsẖwʿ lk rby mqdmaⁿạ lk kl qlby
 fhạ ḥyạty ạ̉mạmk ạ̹dẖ qd krsthạ lsẖkẖṣk
 ạlqrạr- fltʿṭi ʿbdk mn fyḍ rwḥk
 wạmnḥny qwẗ fy kl ḥyn
 fạ̉sẖhd lk wlṣnyʿk wạ̉ʿln ḥqk ạltẖmyn
 2- ʿynạy dạỷmaⁿạ trnw ạ̹lyk nfsy tntẓr fʿl ydyk
 fạ̹nk ạlạ̹lh nbʿ ạlḥyạẗ wmạnḥ ạlrjạʾ ạ̹ly̱ ạlkẖṭạẗ
 3- ʿlmny rby fʿl rḍạk lkymạ ạ̉tbʿn ạ̹tẖr kẖṭạk
 ạ̉ryd rby ạ̉n ạ̉ḥyạ lk dwmaⁿạ mmyzaⁿạ ṣwtk</lyrics>
<title>ạ̉sjd fy kẖsẖwʿ</title>
